{"id": "rjy1665702601052", "title": "$fieldmod", "breadcrumbs": ["Uniface Reference", "ProcScript Reference", "ProcScript: Functions", "$fieldmod"], "url": "https://docs.rocketsoftware.com/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/rjy1665702601052.html", "html": "<html><body><header class=\"zDocsTopicPageHead\"><h1 class=\"css-g931ng\">$fieldmod</h1><div class=\"zDocsTopicActions\" role=\"list\"><div class=\"zDocsBundlePagination\" data-testid=\"next-prev-container\" role=\"listitem\"><div class=\"zDocsPrevTopicButton zDocsPrevTopicButton\"><span class=\"\"><a aria-label=\"Previous:   $fieldinfo \" class=\"\" data-tooltip-content=\"Previous:   $fieldinfo \" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" data-tooltip-open=\"false\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jxo1665703007536.html\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-prev\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-prev\"></use></svg></a></span></div><div class=\"zDocsNextTopicButton zDocsNextTopicButton\"><span class=\"\"><a aria-label=\"Next:   $fieldname \" class=\"\" data-tooltip-content=\"Next:   $fieldname \" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" data-tooltip-open=\"false\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jfn1665702577202.html\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></a></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsMyDocsMenu\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Add to My Topics\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Add to My Topics\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" id=\"addToMyDocsDropdownTrigger\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-bookmark-add\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-bookmark-add\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-bookmark-add\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-bookmark-add\"></use></svg>Add to My Topics</span><div aria-labelledby=\"pdfDropdown\" class=\"dropdown-menu dropdown-menu-right\"><a class=\"zDocsAddTopicButton zDocsMyDocsMenuItem dropdown-item\" href=\"/de-DE/auth/login?redirect=/bundle/uniface_104/page/rjy1665702601052.html?finish_action=mydocs_topic_and_sub\">Add selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsAddTopicButton zDocsMyDocsMenuItem dropdown-item\" href=\"/de-DE/auth/login?redirect=/bundle/uniface_104/page/rjy1665702601052.html?finish_action=mydocs_topic_and_sub_head\">Add Topic &amp; Subtopics with topic head</a><a class=\"zDocsAddTopicButton zDocsMyDocsMenuItem dropdown-item\" href=\"/de-DE/auth/login?redirect=/bundle/uniface_104/page/rjy1665702601052.html?finish_action=mydocs_pub\">Add entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsWatchButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Watch\" class=\"d-lg-flex d-none zDocsSubscribeButton\" data-tooltip-content=\"Watch\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-eye\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-eye\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsSubscribeButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-eye zDocsSubscribeButton\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-eye\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsSubscribeButton\">Watch</span></span></div><div class=\"zDocsExportPdfMenu zDocsExportMenu\" data-testid=\"export-pdf-menu\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Download PDF\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Download PDF\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-pdf\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-pdf\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#ZdExportPDFModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-pdf\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-pdf\"></use></svg>Download PDF</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportTopicButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"singlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportSubtopicsButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"pdfWithChildren\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportBundleButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"wholeBundlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicShare zDocsShareButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Share\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex zDocsShareDialogButton\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Share\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none zDocsShareDialogButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg>Share</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareEmail\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Email Link</span></a><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareLink\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Copy Link</span></a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsFeedback zDocsFeedback zDocsTopicFeedback\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Feedback\" class=\"zDocsFeedbackButton d-none d-lg-flex\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2531638\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-tooltip-content=\"Feedback\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2531638\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Juli 10, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104rjy1665702601052.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/rjy1665702601052.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/rjy1665702601052.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"rjy1665702601052\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      $fieldmod\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"rjy1665702601052___fieldmod_264193\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Return the modification status of a field.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"rjy1665702601052__topic_d83195e1_d83196e1_d83197e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"rjy1665702601052__p_d83198e1_d83199e1_d83200e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$fieldmod</span> { <code class=\"ph codeph\">(</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Field</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">)</code> }</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"rjy1665702601052__topic_d54977e1_d54978e1_d54979e1_d54980e1_d54981e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d641407e75\">\n                       Parameters</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"rjy1665702601052__d6203e20\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Parameters</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"rjy1665702601052__d6203e20__entry__1\">Parameter</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"rjy1665702601052__d6203e20__entry__2\">Data Type</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"rjy1665702601052__d6203e20__entry__3\">Description</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rjy1665702601052__d6203e20__entry__1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Field</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rjy1665702601052__d6203e20__entry__2\">String</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rjy1665702601052__d6203e20__entry__3\">Field name. It can optionally contain a\n                        qualified field name, for example <code class=\"ph codeph\">MYFLD.MYENT</code>. If omitted,\n                        the current field is assumed.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"rjy1665702601052__topic_d54982e1_d54983e1_d54984e1_d54985e1_d54986e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d641407e132\">\n                       \n Return Values\n </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"rjy1665702601052__table_d8549e1_d8550e1_d8551e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 2. </span><span class=\"title\">Values Returned by <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$fieldmod</span>\n</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"rjy1665702601052__table_d8549e1_d8550e1_d8551e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\">\n Value \n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"rjy1665702601052__table_d8549e1_d8550e1_d8551e1__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Meaning</p>\n</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rjy1665702601052__table_d8549e1_d8550e1_d8551e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\">\n 1\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rjy1665702601052__table_d8549e1_d8550e1_d8551e1__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\">\n Modified.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rjy1665702601052__table_d8549e1_d8550e1_d8551e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\">\n 0\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rjy1665702601052__table_d8549e1_d8550e1_d8551e1__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\">\n Not modified.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rjy1665702601052__table_d8549e1_d8550e1_d8551e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\">\n \"\"\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rjy1665702601052__table_d8549e1_d8550e1_d8551e1__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\">\n An error occurred.\n </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"rjy1665702601052__p_d83207e1_d83208e1_d83209e1\">If an error occurs, <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$procerror</span> contains a negative value that identifies the exact error.</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"rjy1665702601052__table_d8552e1_d8553e1_d8554e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 3. </span><span class=\"title\">Values of $procerror Commonly Returned Following Field-Level ProcScript Functions</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"rjy1665702601052__table_d8552e1_d8553e1_d8554e1__entry__1\">Value </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"rjy1665702601052__table_d8552e1_d8553e1_d8554e1__entry__2\">\nError\nconstant\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"rjy1665702601052__table_d8552e1_d8553e1_d8554e1__entry__3\">\nMeaning\n</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rjy1665702601052__table_d8552e1_d8553e1_d8554e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">-1101\n</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rjy1665702601052__table_d8552e1_d8553e1_d8554e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;UPROCERR_FIELD&gt;\n</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rjy1665702601052__table_d8552e1_d8553e1_d8554e1__entry__3\">\nAn incorrect\nfield name was provided; either the field name is not valid syntactically\nor the field is not available in the component.\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"rjy1665702601052__topic_d54987e1_d54988e1_d54989e1_d54990e1_d54991e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d641407e262\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"rjy1665702601052__d6417e20\">Allowed in all component types, except self-contained Reports.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"rjy1665702601052__topic_d54992e1_d54993e1_d54994e1_d54995e1_d54996e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d641407e272\">\n                       Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"rjy1665702601052__d6801e20\">The function is\n\t\tset to <code class=\"ph codeph\">0</code> in the following circumstances:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"rjy1665702601052__d6801e28\">Each time a component is restarted (unless\n\t\t\t <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Component Behavior</span> is set to <code class=\"ph codeph\">Keep component definition and data in\n\t\t\t memory</code>).</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"rjy1665702601052__d6801e37\">By the following ProcScript statements<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"rjy1665702601052__d6801e41\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">clear</span>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"rjy1665702601052__d6801e47\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">erase</span>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"rjy1665702601052__d6801e53\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">release</span>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"rjy1665702601052__d6801e59\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">reload</span>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"rjy1665702601052__d6801e65\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">retrieve</span>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"rjy1665702601052__d6801e72\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">store</span>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"rjy1665702601052__topic_d54997e1_d54998e1_d54999e1_d55000e1_d55001e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d641407e339\">\n                       Events that Modify a Field</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"rjy1665702601052__p_d83225e1_d83226e1_d83227e1\">Events that cause a field to be recognized as\n\t\tmodified include such things as:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"rjy1665702601052__li_d34247e1_d34248e1_d34249e1\">The user entering a retrieve profile in an\n\t\t\t empty field. (This means that <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$fieldmod</span> or <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$fielddbmod</span> can be set to 1  before  a\n\t\t\t <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">retrieve</span> has been performed.) </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"rjy1665702601052__li_d34250e1_d34251e1_d34252e1\">The user changing the value of data that has\n\t\t\t been retrieved. </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"rjy1665702601052__li_d34253e1_d34254e1_d34255e1\">Modification of a non-database occurrence\n\t\t\t made by a ProcScript assignment (<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">=</span>) without the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/init</span> switch.\n\t\t\t </li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"rjy1665702601052__section_ukn_xvy_zbc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d641407e375\">Example: Calculating Total Price </h2>\n<div class=\"div\">\n<p class=\"p\">The following example checks the value of <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$fieldmod</span>\n               for the field DISCOUNT. If the value has been modified, the field TOTAL_PRICE is\n               recalculated. The processing takes place in the leaveModified trigger, as the value\n               of TOTAL_PRICE depends on several fields.</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"rjy1665702601052__pre_fnv_xvy_zbc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">trigger leaveModified \n if ($fieldmod(DISCOUNT) = 1)\n TOTAL_PRICE = DISCOUNT * ORDER_SIZE * UNIT_PRICE\n endif\nend; leaveModified</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ogw1665702600188.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$fieldendmod</a><p>Return the modification status of a field when the field is exited.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2531638\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2531638\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "$fieldmod Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Juli 10, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 $fieldmod Return the modification status of a field. $fieldmod { ( Field ) } Parameters Table 1. Parameters Parameter Data Type Description Field String Field name. It can optionally contain a qualified field name, for example MYFLD.MYENT . If omitted, the current field is assumed. Return Values Table 2. Values Returned by $fieldmod Value Meaning 1 Modified. 0 Not modified. \"\" An error occurred. If an error occurs, $procerror contains a negative value that identifies the exact error. Table 3. Values of $procerror Commonly Returned Following Field-Level ProcScript Functions Value Error constant Meaning -1101 <UPROCERR_FIELD> An incorrect field name was provided; either the field name is not valid syntactically or the field is not available in the component. Use Allowed in all component types, except self-contained Reports. Description The function is set to 0 in the following circumstances: Each time a component is restarted (unless Component Behavior is set to Keep component definition and data in memory ). By the following ProcScript statements clear erase release reload retrieve store Events that Modify a Field Events that cause a field to be recognized as modified include such things as: The user entering a retrieve profile in an empty field. (This means that $fieldmod or $fielddbmod can be set to 1 before a retrieve has been performed.) The user changing the value of data that has been retrieved. Modification of a non-database occurrence made by a ProcScript assignment ( = ) without the /init switch. Example: Calculating Total Price The following example checks the value of $fieldmod for the field DISCOUNT. If the value has been modified, the field TOTAL_PRICE is recalculated. The processing takes place in the leaveModified trigger, as the value of TOTAL_PRICE depends on several fields. trigger leaveModified if ($fieldmod(DISCOUNT) = 1) TOTAL_PRICE = DISCOUNT * ORDER_SIZE * UNIT_PRICE endif end; leaveModified Copy Related Links $fieldendmod Return the modification status of a field when the field is exited. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}